headline: CVS accused of shutting out rival pharmacy hubs in House Judiciary investigation
summary: The company’s massive pharmacy benefit manager changed its rules and weaponized audits to ensure independent pharmacies couldn’t work with competing pharmacy service companies, House Republicans said.
